lader (1.0.0) stable; urgency=medium

  * The first stable released version
  * The utility performs parsing of logic analyzer data, 
    writing the result to an output file, 
    and outputs the length of data packets if it is the same for all packets. 
    To get help with the utility, use --help

 -- JanisRUS <janisrus35@gmail.com>  Tue, 2 Jul 2026 21:57:26 +0300

lader (0.2.0) testing; urgency=medium

  * The algorithm for creating the path to the output file has been changed.
    Now the path to the output file is similar to the path of the input file, 
    unless the path to it is explicitly specified with the -o argument.

